Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.71,0:00:19.04,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Piercing through the Macro sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.57,0:00:25.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,a thunderbolt strikes the Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:30.82,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,To awaken us, the young mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:37.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,the Light struck
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:43.00,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.34,0:00:48.81,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave youths who arise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.02,0:00:52.87,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,and fight to protect their loved ones
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.21,0:00:58.02,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:01.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you love me tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.52,0:01:06.65,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Slicing through the darkness they fly toward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:12.60,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,that blue planet that shines in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:18.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross! Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:24.33,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:47.05,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(82,118)}ROMANESQUE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:20.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Switching over to the main\Npower generator!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.91,0:02:24.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Engine room!\NWhat's the situation down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:30.01,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The power condenser's shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't replace it because\NI don't have the parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:34.11,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the engine itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:38.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I could probably have it fixed\Nin two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.68,0:02:41.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But without a power condenser,\Nit's not gonna run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:46.12,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. Just keep working on\Nengine repairs for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:48.97,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch the channel. I've got\Nsome orders for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:51.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn the volume to maximum.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:52.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:56.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, you bums! Open up those\Nears of yours and listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:03:00.69,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we can get this ship running there's\Nsomething we have to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:04.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur's and my platoons are going\Nto raid an Earth people's factory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.74,0:03:07.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and steal the parts for a reaction engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:09.61,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack teams will move out as soon\Nas preparations are complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:11.26,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:15.49,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make them regret ever giving us culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.85,0:03:19.88,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show those bastards just how\Nwe use the repair techniques
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:22.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,that they taught us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:57.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Planes 2 and 3, visibility is worsening so I'm\Ngoing to change our return flight path.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:01.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Once we're past the waypoint,\Nmove to course 1-2-0.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:13.91,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe asking her out for tea or\Nsomething will improve her mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Major Hayase?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.57,0:04:21.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She finished early and went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.90,0:04:23.19,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Finished early?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:24.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing in for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:27.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... There's nothing to report\Nin the eastern sector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.00,0:04:29.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Patrol unit returning to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:31.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the invoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.11,0:04:41.41,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see, two power condensers\Nfor a reaction engine
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:45.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,plus three J-17s and two dozen\NPF107 supplemental parts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.32,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,to be loaded into Warehouse 3, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.34,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:08.10,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,How are we doing on sales?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.29,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good. We've still only sold eight items.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:14.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I heard that toys sold well at Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.76,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You! The boy over there!\NHow about a model kit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:21.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we're in a bad location.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:23.13,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should move somewhere\Nwhere there are more kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:28.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We just got fired from the cleaner's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do our best to\Nmake some money...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.39,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.61,0:06:18.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,With sales this bad, it's going to be tough\Njust to make it through the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:20.78,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow's Christmas Eve already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.87,0:06:23.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's set up shop in a new place\Nand work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.49,0:06:25.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:27.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Minmay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.89,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure looks like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:32.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Minmay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:41.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.98,0:06:50.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In last night's news, we reported that\Npopular singer Lynn Minmay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:52.62,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,had collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:56.37,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have since learned that she\Ndid not collapse from illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.92,0:07:02.86,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sources close to Miss Minmay state that she\Nhas, in fact, been missing since last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:06.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Minmay stepped out after saying\Nshe was going out for a bit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but she has not returned and her\Nwhereabouts are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:14.63,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Some entertainers speculate this may be related\Nto the disappearance of Lynn Kaifun,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:20.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Minmay's manager, several days ago but\Nwe have yet to receive confirmation of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:31.42,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:41.46,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.74,0:07:50.87,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:57.56,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.70,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Give my regards to Ichijo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.82,0:08:06.79,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:17.00,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you warmed up a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:19.20,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:23.67,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just had it with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:26.94,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All that attention started going to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:32.43,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I knew it, it was like I'd lost\Nall these parts of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.93,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know what I should do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.65,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happens to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.28,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We all go through life,\Nlosing things along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.82,0:08:52.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you still have your songs,\Nso you can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.17,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not enough just to like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to sing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:08:57.91,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.33,0:09:01.06,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't sing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:03.45,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.99,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.52,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Something happened between\Nyou and Kaifun, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:12.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.83,0:09:15.40,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.47,0:09:16.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.74,0:09:21.23,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew each other too well.\NWe'd get mad just looking at each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.83,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,In show business, even among my old friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:31.81,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,no one will listen to me or\Ntake my feelings seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:36.92,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only person who thought about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.36,0:09:38.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.77,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who cared was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:44.30,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if I stayed here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.38,0:09:45.14,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.80,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'd be a bother if I stayed forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.54,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but just for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.68,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anywhere to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.09,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:57.57,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:01.59,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:04.50,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're all right with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.16,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, lady? You feelin' bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:31.60,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Drunk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.84,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I still haven't drunk his share yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.68,0:11:09.82,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,What will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.53,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Bourbon, straight up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.64,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:14.33,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,"...continually dazzling..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:18.58,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"You say I'm..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.61,0:11:23.71,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"falling for him"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.66,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"But I love you more"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:38.38,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Always together on Sunset Beach..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.16,0:11:34.66,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:58.03,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru's place...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.00,0:12:36.47,Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.56,0:13:07.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Major, I could pull over if\Nyou're not feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:09.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right. Keep driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Major Hayase's hung over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:16.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ssshh! Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really really true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:22.42,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not find out at the party today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:27.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do something\Nthat insensitive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.44,0:13:29.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, keep up the "Miss Sensible" routine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:31.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Pfft!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.83,0:13:55.66,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.82,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am. The members of the\Nbridge crew are throwing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.33,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were hoping you could come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.63,0:14:04.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, and why not bring Captain Ichijo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:06.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think he'd come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.86,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But isn't he off today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.37,0:14:11.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in bed with a bad cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Emergency transmission from Onogi City!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin and his men are raiding\Nthe industrial sector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max and Milia Team, scramble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.75,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern patrol units, head to Onogi City\Nand provide support at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.11,0:14:28.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur! Haven't you found it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:31.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All these buildings look the same!\NI can't tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.23,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:36.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not happy with how this\Nis turning out! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of Onogi City!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:42.40,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,A Zentradi gang is attacking the industrial area!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:45.98,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please follow the directions of the military\Nand evacuate immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.77,0:15:02.56,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,They're looking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.00,0:15:05.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing more than conjecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.24,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,but given that our city is home to the\NUN Government Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.32,0:15:11.46,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin's true target is most probably here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:16.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,For a man like him, attacking from\Nthe rear is unthinkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.99,0:15:18.89,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after a reaction engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:20.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.47,0:15:22.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:23.48,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:26.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern sector Valkyrie patrol squadron,\NMax and Milia Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.93,0:15:30.92,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe that Kamujin intends\Nto steal a reaction engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.07,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect the industrial complex that holds\Nthe reaction engine factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.35,0:15:41.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Oigur! He's taking too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.37,0:15:51.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now this is more my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.14,0:15:56.27,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.58,0:16:02.67,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:22.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Lap'Lamiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.47,0:16:23.59,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.79,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We now present some breaking news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:40.30,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,At roughly 7:20 this morning a group of\Nbattle pods began to attack Onogi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:45.22,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The pods are attacking the industrial\Nsector along the city's coastline.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:47.49,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Patrol units are converging on\Nthe city to quell the attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:49.40,MacrossCollide,,0000,0000,0000,,Onogi City? But that's in my sector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:49.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the insurgent troops are more\Npowerful than expected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.54,0:16:51.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,and no one is certain when the\Nsituation will be resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.05,0:16:53.85,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why wasn't I ordered to scramble?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.16,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.46,0:17:03.62,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:21.99,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We hit the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:29.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,W...We're leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.76,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:41.06,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.13,0:17:44.37,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fighting that broke out in\NOnogi City at 8:00 this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.39,0:17:48.26,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,has grown even more intense and there appear\Nto be heavy casualties on both sides
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.38,0:17:50.34,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as among the local populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:10.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.85,0:18:13.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oigur, get ready to move out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.18,0:18:14.31,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:19.63,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is withdrawing!\NThey're heading southwest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.86,0:18:22.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Surround them! If it looks like they'll\Nreach the residential area,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.09,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I authorize the use of missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:37.12,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Milia, we've got to go give the town some cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.21,0:18:41.51,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.70,0:18:59.71,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Old Man Santa.\NThe mission was a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:02.04,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll retrieve Lap'Lamiz and return to base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:04.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for their Christmas present.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:07.38,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I repeat, it's time for their Christmas present!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:22.18,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Max! Milia! Abort pursuit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.32,0:19:24.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to help the people in the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.15,0:19:26.11,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:08.29,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It has already been six hours since\Nthe fighting in Onogi City
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,ended with the withdrawal of the battle pods.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.90,0:20:14.80,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fires we once thought would\Nreduce the city to ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.85,0:20:19.19,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,are finally under control, and the\Nsituation has become calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:24.84,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there have been many injuries and\Nfatalities among the military and civilians alike, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:46.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,...so tender and mild
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:55.07,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep in heavenly peace
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:21:03.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep in heavenly peace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:11.85,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent night, holy night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:20.10,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Shepherds quake at the sight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:28.72,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavenly hosts sing Hallelujah
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.74,0:21:27.74,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard from Vanessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:30.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me why I wasn't\Ncalled for the scramble.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:37.11,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Glories stream from Heaven afar
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:35.32,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you lie and say I was sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:40.45,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, you should always make\Nsure your door is shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:45.46,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ the Savior is born
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.28,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.60,0:21:52.97,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Christ the Savior is born
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:22:01.60,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent night, holy night
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:09.51,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Son of God, love's pure light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:17.74,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Radiant beams from Thy holy face
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:26.09,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,With the dawn of redeeming grace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:21.05,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.83,0:22:23.50,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.83,0:22:25.36,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.32,0:22:34.48,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, Lord at Thy birth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.00,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go freshen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.84,0:22:41.30,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus, Lord at Thy birth
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:48.61,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness... You're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:55.57,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Hikaru, quit the military.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.88,0:23:00.01,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear waiting for you\Nlike this, worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:10.35,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Hikaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:13.83,*Macross1,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry Christmas, Minmay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.99,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(88,109)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.99,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(337,454)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.00,0:23:37.61,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin, having now obtained a functioning\Nwarship attempts to settle things
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.70,0:23:40.66,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,once and for all by plunging headfirst\Ninto the grounded Macross.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:43.87,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Dimension Fortress Macross,\Nthe final episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.17,0:23:46.67,narration,,0000,0000,0000,,"Farewell to Tenderness"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:47.04,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(103,144)}Farewell to Tenderness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.15,0:24:07.70,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't follow it anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:14.45,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow you cast as you run away
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.79,0:24:21.05,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,We all keep running until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.26,0:24:28.78,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,But we still can't see the goal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.14,0:24:35.50,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us after today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.72,0:24:41.37,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,What awaits us beyond tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.65,0:24:48.90,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, I keep running toward
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.13,0:25:00.16,songM,,0000,0000,0000,,The light that shines so far away
